#

Spicy Grilled Chicken Burrito with Mango Salsa

$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

BurritoMexican CuisineSpicyGrilled Chicken

Description

A delicious and hearty burrito filled with spicy grilled chicken and topped with a refreshing mango salsa for a burst of flavor.

Ingredients

  • Flour Tortilla: 1 large
  • Grilled Chicken Breast: 6 oz
  • Black Beans: 1/2 cup
  • Shredded Cheddar Cheese: 1/2 cup
  • Sour Cream: 2 tbsp
  • Salsa: 1/4 cup
  • Mango: 1/2 cup, diced
  • Red Onion: 1/4 cup, finely chopped
  • Cilantro: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Lime Juice: 1 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 1 tbsp
